WEBVTT

00:00.780 --> 00:01.960
Alan, Shirley.

00:01.960 --> 00:02.600
Lorraine.

00:02.600 --> 00:05.140
I suppose it was inevitable
we'd finally bump heads a bit.

00:05.180 --> 00:06.930
This was just assigned
to us by the court.

00:06.970 --> 00:09.250
Indigent client— old lawyer
jumped in front of a bus—

00:09.290 --> 00:10.600
now he needs a new one.

00:10.640 --> 00:11.590
Did you not commit this crime?

00:11.630 --> 00:13.360
Why aren't you pleading this case out?

00:13.400 --> 00:14.010
He's innocent.

00:14.050 --> 00:15.060
Alan, you take over.

00:15.100 --> 00:16.630
Me? What about Jerry?

00:16.630 --> 00:18.630
If there's a hope, it's not Katie Lloyd.

00:18.670 --> 00:20.680
Katie Lloyd will be my lawyer.

00:20.680 --> 00:25.230
Dr Rivers, several people have stated that
Joseph Washington seemed obsessed with your wife.

00:25.270 --> 00:27.550
Did you ever see indications of this?
–No.

00:27.590 --> 00:29.834
He always struck me as a nice man.

